{"tid":786720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(賴） 沙中線爆醜聞　拉布早埋禍根","createTime":"2018-08-20T06:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T06:55:43.000Z","uid":78440,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4de54e8212f7f3d2a15a9917bc62335216c2b3e5","tid":786720,"uid":78440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"點解可以將港鐵工程出問題拉落去拉布到？<br />\n<br />\n我真係讀得書少，拉布真係搞到工程停晒？ <br />\n工程停晒同剪鋼筋、改圖則、監管不力又有咩關係？ <br />\n<br />\n雖然我都唔想大大聲講中資建築商一定差，意大利橋都一樣會塌，咁事實係天價造左兩條線 （忽然醒起有仲有條港珠澳），造到呢樣唔掂果樣唔掂<br />\n<br />\n係唔係年年加價就係養班垃圾高層、垃圾GT、垃圾工程撚？ <br />\n<br />\n求真相"},{"pid":"2b73dbfd83b0038187b86d2923f63c7bd753b98f","tid":786720,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"其實係佔中的錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54be4dcaf124f9dbb7562ec68ebf87bcdf8f79dc","tid":786720,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"以香港政府既才能 同中央政府既英明領導下<br />\n<br />\n沙中線 高鐵線點會有問題呢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要求沙中線正常復工，如常係2018第4季開車<br />\n<br />\n要求高鐵第3季開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不得延誤"},{"pid":"419efa4dd8ae3c7083a09a58a0cd34c1ed0b57ae","tid":786720,"uid":36296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:48:00.000Z","msg":"關撚事咩 想轉移視線 等啲冇腦廢中有個藉口屌拉布屌後生"},{"pid":"b9fa347cc9b6ab158399f98e8ea636fdafbcb1d1","tid":786720,"uid":82658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/191736_35cdf1cb3d495fa959436795cfab8abf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F191736_35cdf1cb3d495fa959436795cfab8abf.jpg&h=759c4b01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cb97e783c8ba8db934b8